title: Pieta Brown - 2013-08-31, MN State Fair, Falcon Heights (AUD)
description:
Pieta Brown
MN State Fair- Heritage Sqaure Stage 
Falcon Heights, MN	
8-31-13


-Audience Recording using Zoom H2 rear internal mics >SD Card>PC>Adobe Audition>CD Wave Editor (split tracks)>TLH>FLAC Level 8 
-"A "MN Gneiss" recording" 
-Feel free to re-master, share on any other torrent site, convert to MP3, just never ever sell it. Also, if you like this show, why not support the artist by buying their music? 


Outdoor concert at the fair, so some noise in the background during quiter parts. Some buzzing in quiter parts as well, this is not a recording fault, it was coming from some electrical wires nearby. Show was ended early due to lightning in the area and a light rain, it was pretty windy at points but it doesn't sound like it caused any problems with the recording.


Pieta Brown
